Godavarman Thirumulkpad vs Union Of India & Ors on 12 December, 1996
Indian Kanoon - http://indiankanoon.org/doc/298957/ 36. Each State Government should within two months, file a report regarding:-
(i) the number of saw mills, veneer and plywood mills actually operating within the
State, with particulars of their real ownership;
     (ii) the   licensed    and   actual
     capacity of  these mills  for stock
     and sawing;
     (iii)     their  proximity  to  the
     nearest forest;
     (iv) their source of timber. 7.
